description:
Strip your clothing system back to essentials. These soft shell pants score a place on your gear list for dawn-to-dusk missions. The design allows easy movement on vertical terrain, and if the weather breaks en route, the fabric coating sheds light rain or snow.Breathable double-weave soft shell with DWR finish that sheds snow and light rain.OppoSet waist adjustment system sits comfortably under a hipbelt or harness.Articulated knees let you high-step with ease.Pockets are accessible when wearing a pack or harness.Narrow hem has a single cuff and tie-down loops compatible with alpine boots.

